I"<p>It’s a wonderful world, hidden in plain sight. Here there are some resources for inspiration and study.</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="vignelli.com" rel="noopener" target="_blank">The Vignelli Canon</a>, a book on design, <strong>the</strong> book on design, by <a href="https://ilpost.it" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Massimo Vignelli</a>. This book inspired me, so much that it completely changed how I see the world (and made me fall in love with Typography).</li>
  <li><a href="https://www.ilpost.it/2020/02/09/font-preferiti-scrittori-italiani/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">I font preferiti dagli scrittori italiani</a>, article by <a href="https://ilpost.it" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Il Post</a>.</li>
  <li>Articles tagged with “<a href="https://www.ilpost.it/tag/font/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">fonts</a>” on <a href="https://ilpost.it" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Il Post</a>.</li>
  <li><a href="http://webtypography.net/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Web Typography</a>, a website focused on typography on the Web, <a href="http://clagnut.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Richard Rutter</a>.</li>
  <li>Google Fonts <a href="https://fonts.google.com/about" rel="noopener" target="_blank">About page</a>.</li>
  <li>Font Forge <a href="http://designwithfontforge.com/en-US/index.html" rel="noopener" target="_blank">guide</a>.</li>
  <li>The <a href="https://fontlibrary.org/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Font Library</a>’s <a href="https://fontlibrary.org/en/guidebook" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Guidebook</a>.
